cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper specifically focuses on the trade-off between model-based and model-free learning in reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also applies the proposed method to Atari games, which suggests that it may fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as well. Finally, the paper deals with decision-making problems, which could potentially fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
